- change setInterval function to this:
```
setInterval(function () {

    for (var i = 0; i < 50; i++) {
        data.push(randomData());
    }

    myChart.setOption({
        series: [{
            data: data
        }]
    });
}, 200);
```

This will happen with any chart component, because for each pixel on the screen, the average value of the points below has to be calculated - for about 1200 px every 200ms (see above).

